Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不一定是攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這不是谷風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你們確實是
